ous criticism. Jeff Bezos, Elon Musk, Carta&#8217;s Henry Ward, and Stripe&=
#8217;s Collison Brothers are Worldbuilders. </p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a=
; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Hinkie is a World=
builder. </p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px=
; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Hinkie&#8217;s Process, his three year term as the Si=
xers&#8217; GM, is textbook Worldbuilding. He had a vision for an NBA Champ=
ionship in Philadelphia, charted a probabilistic path to get there, and the=
n did the unconventional, criticism-attracting things required to make it h=
appen.</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; m=
argin: 0 0 1em 0;"><strong>If Hinkie&#8217;s Process is textbook Worldbuild=
ing, his <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFUDuO7CAQPM0QWvzsxQ=
HBJnsNhKE9RoPBguZZfqdfxhOs1OpSf0tVziI8c7n0kSuSVqGY4DWbuBKjnInX0jM1KhKqWQvAb=
